#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.bitwise_xor:63
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "範例"

#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.bitwise_xor:70
msgid ""
"The number 13 is represented by ``00001101``. Likewise, 17 is represented by "
"``00010001``.  The bit-wise XOR of 13 and 17 is therefore ``00011100``, or "
"28:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.bitwise_xor:89
msgid ""
"The ``^`` operator can be used as a shorthand for ``np.bitwise_xor`` on "
"ndarrays."
msgstr ""

